n\n## Getting Started\nTo get started, add the Power-Up and then select Burn Down the List from the list action menu.\n![Select the Burn Down the List action.](https://bdtl.burndown-analytics.com/list-action-anim.gif)\n\nA configuration menu for the initial burn down chart will allow you to set the project duration and expected point count.\nThe duration can be changed at any time by modifying the card due date, and the expected point count can be changed by updating the number in the list name.\n![Configure initial chart parameters.](https://bdtl.burndown-analytics.com/initial-config.png)\n\nPoints for the project estimate or for completed task cards can be specified by including any number in the name, optionally surrounded by braces. For example the following names all indicate a project or task card with 200 estimated points:\n\n - \"My Big Project (200)\"\n - \"My Big 200 Point Project\" \n - \"{200} Paint the shed\"\n - \"(200) Mow the lawn\"\n\nAs completed cards are moved into the burn down list, the chart will update with the new point count for the day. Completed cards need a point count in their title, as well as a due date that is marked complete.\n\n![A 5 point card is brought into the list and the points remaining count for the day is reduced by 5.](https://bdtl.burndown-analytics.com/card-completion.gif)\n\n## Pricing\nAfter a free 5-day trial, $6.85 per month enables unlimited burn down lists across an unlimited number of boards for the entire team.\n\n## Questions\nPlease email bdtl@burndown-analytics.com and we'll answer any questions you may have.\n\n----\n\nFlame Icon made by [Freepik](\"https://www.freepik.com/\") from [www.flaticon.com](https://www.flaticon.com/) is licensed by [CC 3.0 BY](http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/)\n","overview":"High visibility burn down charts"}},{"id":"5c75708a72eecc4565ecacf5","idOrganizationOwner":"59fb30baa0e270f883ddd8f6","author":"Unito","capabilities":["authorization-status","board-buttons","callback